Overhaulin' - Season 8, Episode 6




Doug's 1955 Ford Thunderbird

Musician Doug is the proud owner of a '55 Ford Thunderbird. When Doug is accused of torching his T-Bird for insurance money, he is undeniably upset. When it is revealed that his car is heading to the Overhaulin' shop, Doug is singing a different tune.
